events.name: Oklahoma Sooners at Iowa State Cyclones

headlines.description: Baker Mayfield threw for 328 yards and four touchdowns and 14th-ranked Oklahoma held off Iowa State 34-24 on Thursday night for its sixth straight victory.
headlines.shortLinkText: Baker Mayfield, No. 14 Sooners hold off Iowa State 34-24

video.headline: Mayfield, Oklahoma hold off Iowa State

headlines.description: Isaiah Oliver returned a punt 68 yards for a score with 5:27 remaining and No. 15 Colorado overcame eight personal-foul penalties to beat UCLA 20-10 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 15 Colorado squeaks by UCLA 20-10 despite penalties

headlines.description: Quinton Maxwell passed for 236 yards and two touchdowns and ran for 50 yards and another score to help Ohio beat Buffalo 34-10 on Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ohio builds big lead early, holds off Buffalo 34-10

events.name: Arkansas State Red Wolves at Georgia State Panthers

headlines.description: Johnston White had two touchdown runs, and Arkansas State blocked two kicks and scored on two returns to beat Georgia State 31-16 on Thursday night.
